headline: Why Oracle Stock Zoomed Nearly 13% Higher This Week
summary: On the back of positive remarks from the company's CEO and bolstered by an apparent deal with a major artificial intelligence (AI) developer, the stock's price resolutely headed north.  And although the OpenAI report is so far unconfirmed by Oracle, it also sounds like a potential money-spinner for the company.

headline: 3 Software Stocks to Keep an Eye On
summary: From commerce to culture, software is digitizing every aspect of our lives. This secular theme makes SaaS companies attractive investment candidates but also comes with higher valuations that cause volatility. Unfortunately, the rich prices have haunted them over the past six months as the industry has shed 2.3%. This performance was discouraging since the S&P 500 returned 5%.
